rComments: I found him to be clear and interesting. I liked it when he told about real life experiences. The guest lecturers were well prepared and experts in their field

Despite what you may have heard:this is NOT an easy class! Expect to MEMORIZE 100's of slides!! Midterms and final exam had questions about things that were not covered in class, nor were they in the notes. Also, lots of guest speakers who make up more than half of the class notes (disorganized). I would not recommend this class to anyone.

The most boring prof EVER!  I never seen a class with that much slides!  Without exagerating, he (and boring guest lecturer) covered at least 1200 slides in the semester!  This was supposed to be an easy class!  And the prof is kinda full of himself too...
